Experiment_Feedback: Interesting study. However, was frustrating when i would click so fast that i registered as a double click at times.

One of the issues with Psychological research today is the vast majority of it is people carrying out studies simply because they found a 'gap' in the literature. In actuality, some things are simply not worth studying. Unfortunately, this study appears to fall into this camp.
